{"tid":550913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"袁國勇：流感會持續數周　正研究噴鼻式疫苗　擬找中國公司生產","createTime":"2018-02-05T07:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T01:13:39.000Z","uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1e912e564198f7e9785a88221af577dbb197c3b6","tid":550913,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:54:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">袁國勇：流感會持續數周　正研究噴鼻式疫苗　擬找中國公司生產</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180204/s00001/b1faeff30488871d0727297f0057b70f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180204%2Fs00001%2Fb1faeff30488871d0727297f0057b70f.jpg&h=64343d80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冬季流感嚴重，香港大學微生物學系講座教授袁國勇在商台節目指出，流感會持續數星期，乙型流感後會有甲型流感，3月至4月春夏交替時或有甲型H3N2。他呼籲市民盡快接種流感疫苗，特別是長者及兒童。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇指出，因為流感疫苗要每年接種，而且不是100%保護率，故此很多人不願注射：「呢個諗法係錯。」他指，注射疫苗後就算患病，病情亦會減輕，出現併發症機會低，死亡風險亦會降低。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇表示，目前歐美流行一種毋須注射的噴鼻式疫苗，但因為香港市場小，外國藥物公司不欲將有關藥物銷售給香港。他指，香港大學已經製作了相關疫苗種子，希望找到內地公司生產，並做臨牀測試，但需時處理。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，因為香港監管制度跟從外國，藥物跟足外國審批，衛生署自行審批本地生產的藥物過程很漫長。他指，最終可能先經內地食物及藥物質檢總局審批，希望在自己65歲退休前完成。<br />\n<br />\n對於政府的5億元臨時撥款，袁國勇稱「好感激政府將之前拎走的5億，畀返醫管局」。他又指，政府過去幾年給予很多資源重建醫院，但他認為香港人向上流動愈來愈慢，窮困階層愈來愈多，公共醫院需求增大，希望政府給醫管局500億元營運基金：「趁有錢要為未來投資。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180204/s00001/1517710581011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180204%2Fs00001%2F1517710581011&d=lcuFvZK4NcesZK%2FZ6r0c4Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=c9e76cfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180204%2Fs00001%2F1517710581011&h=29f94468\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180204/s00001/1517710581011</a>"},{"pid":"56ed3b021e0af464c9cb8bd45339c82a5673ac7b","tid":550913,"uid":41317,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:57:09.000Z","msg":"好感激政府將<span style=\"color: red;\">之前拎走的5億</span>，畀返醫管局"},{"pid":"854eb492e97305f1c82c9b64fec820374409a47e","tid":550913,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d520edc96d05e21824fc6e29e0f016b44cfc9a2","tid":550913,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:52:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1985d2475adde4619dee247b6741267ae5303719","tid":550913,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:53:51.000Z","msg":"中國人制更加冇人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6db37abe36dfa45180156ff7e12e2f6b36c036e","tid":550913,"uid":4285,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:54:07.000Z","msg":"中國製？ 不了<br />\n<br />\n你打曬佢啦"},{"pid":"2b57069c17b67413703ab39327b16aac42d4c7b2","tid":550913,"uid":111253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:55:11.000Z","msg":"好鬼喎，停課，吹行疫情，引你打支那疫苗"},{"pid":"a2ad200fe8226ca40203487f8c1221f96a78433a","tid":550913,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b57069c17b67413703ab39327b16aac42d4c7b2","tid":550913,"uid":111253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:55:11.000Z","msg":"好鬼喎，停課，吹行疫情，引你打支那疫苗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:59:44.000Z","msg":"喂 咁大陸人都要搵錢架 你咁水魚唔搵你搵邊個"},{"pid":"ae6c6497386fea29d39e22bacb9eddfc91e9a138","tid":550913,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T06:00:20.000Z","msg":"支持優先俾廢老同綜援新移民用"},{"pid":"9484935129f02a1a1311ca83ded9d54c14a822bb","tid":550913,"uid":18912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"56ed3b021e0af464c9cb8bd45339c82a5673ac7b","tid":550913,"uid":41317,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"